text_blocks.text:
The purpose of the sector goals of the NSDS, including the energy goal, is to enable the achievement of Nauru’s overall vision and the long-term goals below:
* Stable, trustworthy, fiscally responsible government;
* Provision of enhanced social, infrastructure and utilities services;
* Development of an economy based on multiple sources of revenue;
* Rehabilitation of mined out lands for livelihood sustainability;
* Development of domestic food production.
